      "text": "Material Design (codenamed Quantum Paper) is a design language developed by Google. Expanding upon the \"card\" motifs that debuted in Google Now, Material Design makes more liberal use of grid-based layouts, responsive animations and transitions, padding, and depth effects such as lighting and shadows - [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Material_Design wikipedia]"
